<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
        background-color: #f8f8f8;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
      h1 {
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: bold;
        text-align: center;
        margin: 0 0 20px;
        color: #00458B;
      }
      p {
        margin: 0 0 20px;
        color: #333;
      }
      .otp-code {
        font-size: 28px;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #00458B;
      }
      .cta-button {
        display: inline-block;
        background-color: #00458B;
        color: #fff;
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: bold;
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        border-radius: 4px;
        margin-top: 20px;
      }
      .cta-button:hover {
        background-color: #003366;
      }
      .signature {
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #333;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Your OTP for Account Verification</h1>

    <p>Dear {{name}},</p>

    <p>Thank you for creating an account with our platform. To complete the account verification process, please enter the following OTP (One-Time Password) on the verification page:</p>

    <p className="otp-code">{{OTP}}</p>

    <p>Please note that this OTP is only valid for the next 2 minutes. If you do not verify your account within this time frame, you will need to request a new OTP.</p>

    <p>If you did not request this OTP, please ignore this email or contact our support team immediately at {{our_contact_information}}.</p>

    <p>Thank you for choosing our platform. We look forward to serving you!</p>

    <p className="signature">Best regards,<br>
    {{our_name}}</p>
  </body>
</html>
